subSubSection.paragraph:
Female.
Length (
1.62–1.94 mm
). Width (
0.93–1.31 mm
). As for the male except rostral scales only at base, not reaching antennal insertions, surface not rugose; scape shorter than desmomeres 1 to 3; elytral humeri rounded, several tubercles before elytral declivity; femora unarmed.
